ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    Lister.RequiredValues && Lister.DisplayMode = DisplayMode.Edit && IsEmpty(Items),
    Lister.Style.Palette.Warning,
    Color.Transparent
)

Self.PaddingTop + Self.PaddingBottom + 42 + If(
    ctnActions_Lister.Visible,
    52,
    0
) + If(
    CountRows(Items) < 3,
    96,
    CountRows(Items) * 32
)
